New Revision: 333287
URL: http://svnweb.freebsd.org/changeset/ports/333287

Log:
  www/adzap: fix for perl 5.16

  - Fix for perl 5.16
  - Add LICENSE (BSD)
  - Add DOCS and EXAMPLES options
  - Pass maintainership to submitter

  PR:		ports/183768
  Submitted by:	Horia Racoviceanu <horia racoviceanu.com>

Added:
  head/www/adzap/files/patch-scripts_squid_redirect-nodata   (contents, props changed)
Modified:
  head/www/adzap/Makefile
  head/www/adzap/pkg-descr
